      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TORI KEEPING (1) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 17.26 beating Ita Keeping. Goes very well from this draw with four wins and two minor placings from nine starts. Great chance again. SPEEDY ED (3) boasts a strong record this journey here with three wins and three minors from seven tries. Hit the frame latest (17.33) when third at this track in a Grade 4. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. ROSETTA STREET (2) quickly away to win over the 300m at this track two runs back then raced on speed again when finishing second at this track last start. Expected to be in this for a long way. ERAMOSA (6) placed out of the same box last time out - worth some thought.",
